headline: 3 Diversified Chemical Stocks to Escape Demand Headwinds
summary: Soft demand in specific markets and the sluggishness in China and Europe pose headwinds for the Zacks Chemicals Diversified industry. APD, DD and EMN are poised to navigate the industry challenges.
